          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sports Bets Collection Tax Correction Act</strong></p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to prohibit the imposition of a tax on any wager on a sporting event if that wager is authorized under the law of the state in which it is accepted.</p>]]></text>
